Class ReceivedPacketNumbers

java.lang.Object
  freenet.support.ReceivedPacketNumbers

public class ReceivedPacketNumbers
extends Object

Author:
amphibian Tracks which packet numbers we have received. Implemented as a sorted list since this is simplest and it's unlikely it will be very long in practice. The 512- packet window provides a practical limit.
